---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ru">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<section class="hero">
				<div class="hero-content">
					<p class="hero-tag">AI Digest</p>
					<h1>Дайджест об&nbsp;AI, которому не&nbsp;скучно</h1>
					<p class="hero-sub">
						Свежие модели, инструменты и&nbsp;исследования —
						коротко, по-человечески, как&nbsp;друг, который в&nbsp;теме.
					</p>
					<a href="/blog" class="cta-btn">Читать дайджест →</a>
				</div>
				<div class="hero-deco" aria-hidden="true">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 140 140" width="140" height="140" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<g stroke="rgba(35, 55, 255, 0.35)" stroke-width="1.4" fill="none">
							<line x1="22" y1="34" x2="70" y2="70" />
							<line x1="22" y1="34" x2="70" y2="22" />
							<line x1="70" y1="22" x2="118" y2="34" />
							<line x1="118" y1="34" x2="70" y2="70" />
							<line x1="22" y1="106" x2="70" y2="70" />
							<line x1="22" y1="106" x2="70" y2="118" />
							<line x1="70" y1="118" x2="118" y2="106" />
							<line x1="118" y1="106" x2="70" y2="70" />
							<line x1="22" y1="34" x2="22" y2="106" />
							<line x1="118" y1="34" x2="118" y2="106" />
						</g>
						<g fill="#2337ff">
							<circle cx="70" cy="70" r="6" />
							<circle cx="22" cy="34" r="4.5" opacity="0.85" />
							<circle cx="70" cy="22" r="4.5" opacity="0.85" />
							<circle cx="118" cy="34" r="4.5" opacity="0.85" />
							<circle cx="22" cy="106" r="4.5" opacity="0.85" />
							<circle cx="70" cy="118" r="4.5" opacity="0.85" />
							<circle cx="118" cy="106" r="4.5" opacity="0.85" />
						</g>
					</svg>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="topics">
				<p class="topics-heading">О чём пишем</p>
				<div class="topics-grid">
					<div class="topic-card">
						<svg class="topic-icon" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
							<circle cx="14" cy="14" r="11" fill="none" stroke="#2337ff" stroke-width="1.4" opacity="0.5" />
							<circle cx="14" cy="14" r="2.4" fill="#2337ff" />
							<circle cx="6" cy="9" r="1.8" fill="#2337ff" opacity="0.7" />
							<circle cx="22" cy="9" r="1.8" fill="#2337ff" opacity="0.7" />
							<circle cx="6" cy="19" r="1.8" fill="#2337ff" opacity="0.7" />
							<circle cx="22" cy="19" r="1.8" fill="#2337ff" opacity="0.7" />
							<g stroke="#2337ff" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.5">
								<line x1="14" y1="14" x2="6" y2="9" />
								<line x1="14" y1="14" x2="22" y2="9" />
								<line x1="14" y1="14" x2="6" y2="19" />
								<line x1="14" y1="14" x2="22" y2="19" />
							</g>
						</svg>
						<h3>Языковые модели</h3>
						<p>GPT, Claude, Llama — кто что зарелизил и как это менять рабочие процессы.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="topic-card">
						<svg class="topic-icon" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
							<polyline points="9,8 4,14 9,20" fill="none" stroke="#2337ff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
							<polyline points="19,8 24,14 19,20" fill="none" stroke="#2337ff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
							<line x1="16" y1="6" x2="12" y2="22" stroke="#2337ff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" />
						</svg>
						<h3>Инструменты для разработчиков</h3>
						<p>IDE, агенты, SDK, MCP — что появилось и куда это встраивать.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="topic-card">
						<svg class="topic-icon" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
							<rect x="7" y="7" width="14" height="14" rx="2" fill="none" stroke="#2337ff" stroke-width="1.6" />
							<rect x="11" y="11" width="6" height="6" rx="1" fill="#2337ff" opacity="0.85" />
							<g stroke="#2337ff" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round">
								<line x1="11" y1="3" x2="11" y2="7" />
								<line x1="14" y1="3" x2="14" y2="7" />
								<line x1="17" y1="3" x2="17" y2="7" />
								<line x1="11" y1="21" x2="11" y2="25" />
								<line x1="14" y1="21" x2="14" y2="25" />
								<line x1="17" y1="21" x2="17" y2="25" />
								<line x1="3" y1="11" x2="7" y2="11" />
								<line x1="3" y1="14" x2="7" y2="14" />
								<line x1="3" y1="17" x2="7" y2="17" />
								<line x1="21" y1="11" x2="25" y2="11" />
								<line x1="21" y1="14" x2="25" y2="14" />
								<line x1="21" y1="17" x2="25" y2="17" />
							</g>
						</svg>
						<h3>Инфраструктура и&nbsp;железо</h3>
						<p>GPU, дата-центры, чипы — на чём всё это считается и сколько стоит.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="topic-card">
						<svg class="topic-icon" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
							<line x1="3" y1="24" x2="25" y2="24" stroke="#2337ff" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" />
							<rect x="5" y="16" width="4" height="8" fill="#2337ff" opacity="0.55" />
							<rect x="12" y="11" width="4" height="13" fill="#2337ff" opacity="0.75" />
							<rect x="19" y="6" width="4" height="18" fill="#2337ff" />
						</svg>
						<h3>Исследования и&nbsp;бенчмарки</h3>
						<p>arXiv, бенчи, новые методы — что работает на самом деле, а что красивая презентация.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.hero {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
		gap: 2rem;
		padding: 3rem 0 4rem;
	}
	.hero-content {
		flex: 1;
	}
	.hero-tag {
		font-size: 0.72rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.12em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
	}
	.hero h1 {
		font-size: 2.8rem;
		line-height: 1.1;
		margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
	}
	.hero-sub {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		line-height: 1.65;
		margin: 0 0 2rem;
		max-width: 460px;
	}
	.cta-btn {
		display: inline-block;
		background: var(--accent);
		color: #fff;
		text-decoration: none;
		padding: 0.65em 1.5em;
		border-radius: 8px;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 1rem;
		transition: opacity 0.15s;
	}
	.cta-btn:hover {
		color: #fff;
		opacity: 0.85;
	}
	.hero-deco {
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.topics {
		padding: 3rem 0 2rem;
		border-top: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
	}
	.topics-heading {
		font-size: 0.72rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.12em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
	}
	.topics-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: 1rem;
	}
	.topic-card {
		padding: 1.4rem 1.5rem;
		border: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
		border-radius: 12px;
		background: #fff;
	}
	.topic-icon {
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}
	.topic-card h3 {
		font-size: 1rem;
		margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
		color: rgb(var(--black));
	}
	.topic-card p {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		line-height: 1.5;
		margin: 0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.hero {
			flex-direction: column-reverse;
			gap: 1.5rem;
			padding: 2rem 0 3rem;
		}
		.hero h1 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}
		.hero-deco {
			align-self: center;
		}
		.topics-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
